    <text>
        <body>
            
            <div1 type="letter">
                
                <pb facs="nei.j4c.34.23-24_0001a" />
                <note type="curatorial">Aly Collection</note>
                
       
                <fw type="letterhead">
                Skyrim Farm                    <hi rend="caps">JOHN G. NEIHARDT</hi>
                    <lb/>
                Route 7
                    <lb/>
                Columbia, Mo.  
                </fw>
                
                <opener>
                <dateline>Nov. 25, '61</dateline>
                
                
                <salute>Dear Bower:</salute>
                </opener>
                <p>Many thanks again! It <hi rend="underline">would</hi> be bully if Mott could manage to do the article &#8212; and he would do a corker; but I wonder if he is in a position to take on the job. He is reasonably well, I think, and he certainly is my friend (he has been for 46 years!) But I'm afraid he's crowded with work.</p>
                
                <p>On Dec. 10 his portrait will be unveiled at a testimonial dinner. The painting (by Ned Etheridge) will hang in the School 
                    
                    <pb facs="nei.j4c.34.23-24_0001b"/>
                    <fw type="authorial">-2-</fw>
                    
                    of Journalism with the other Deans. I'm happy about this; He <hi rend="underline">is</hi> a dear man, and he has been a great booster for my work.</p>
             
                <p>My bust will be unveiled in the Senate Chamber of the Capitol Building in Lincoln, Nebraska, on Dec. 7 at 11 <hi rend="caps">A. M.</hi> We'll drive up &#8212; the girls, Lyn, Gail, and I. &#8212;</p>
                
                <p>I think of you dear peoples very often, and I fancy myself walking about the house.</p>
               
                <p>I <hi rend="underline">do</hi> deeply <del>appreciate</del>
                    
                    <fw type="curatorial">23</fw>
                    <pb facs="nei.j4c.43.23-24_0002"/>
                    <fw type="authorial">-3</fw>
                    
                    appreciate my "other home"</p>
                    
                    <p>Be good to yourself and don't work too d -- hard.</p>
                    
                    <p>Prost!</p>
                <closer>
                <salute>Affectionately</salute>
                
                <signed>John N.</signed>
                </closer>
                
            </div1>
            
            
            
